These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, june, february, april, july, march, november
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
There 7 different types of food: orange, cucumber, pomegranate, zucchini, radish, broccoli, pumpkin
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, motorbike, scooter, skateboard, trike, van
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 3. the person driving the bike is the person eating radish##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
16. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
17. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
19. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
20. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Birthday      | february    | october     | november  | march   | april | july      | june          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Food         | orange | cucumber | radish | broccoli | pomegranate   | zucchini     | pumpkin |
| Transport     | van      | trike   | bike   | motorbike  | scooter  | skateboard | jet-ski       |

