10. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the coach is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the ship##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
14. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
