There 7 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, grapefruit, grapes, nectarine, peas, zucchini
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, metal, pop, punk, trance, blues, gospel
City: nizza, rome, colone, berlin, liverpool, new-york, miami
 1. the person drinking juice is the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the fan of metal is the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person eating zucchini is the person traveling to colone##1
12. the person eating cranberry is the person traveling to liverpool##1
13. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the fan of punk##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the fan of blues##1
15. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is the person traveling to colone##1
18. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
19. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
20. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
21. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2      |      3      |       4       |     5     |    6    |    7     |
